OL,3,CNext government must close anti-
OL,4,Ccorruption 'loopholes', say MPs
OL,6,FThe next government should commit to
OL,7,Fclosing "loopholes" in Britain's anti-
OL,8,Fcorruption laws to ensure the UK is
OL,9,Fnot a haven for dirty money, a cross-
OL,10,Fparty group of MPs has said.
OL,12,FIn a manifesto published on Wednesday,
OL,13,Fmembers of the All-Party Parliamentary
OL,14,FGroup (APPG) on Anti-Corruption and
OL,15,FResponsible Tax said the winner of
OL,16,Fthis year's election would have a
OL,17,F"unique chance for global leadership"
OL,18,Fon tackling economic crime.
