OL,3,CNext government must close anti-
OL,4,Ccorruption 'loopholes', say MPs
OL,6,F"The next Parliament must continue the
OL,7,Ffight against our dirty money
OL,8,Fepidemic."
OL,10,FIn its manifesto, the APPG called for
OL,11,Fgreater transparency of company and
OL,12,Fproperty ownership, including closing
OL,13,F"loopholes" that allow owners to
OL,14,F"hide" behind trusts and ensuring the
OL,15,FUK's Overseas Territories and Crown
OL,16,FDependencies bring in public registers
OL,17,Fof company ownership.
