OL,4,Ccorruption 'loopholes', say MPs
OL,6,FThe MPs also called for a tightening
OL,7,Fof anti-money laundering regulations,
OL,8,Ffinding ways to legally seize frozen
OL,9,Fassets, and increased resources for
OL,10,Fenforcement through reinvesting fines
OL,11,Fin an "economic crime-fighting fund".
OL,13,FConservative MP Nigel Mills, who co-
OL,14,Fchairs the APPG, said: "Economic crime
OL,15,Fis corrosive, and it impacts all of
OL,16,Four daily lives.
