OL,3,CNext government must close anti-
OL,4,Ccorruption 'loopholes', say MPs
OL,6,F"Honest people and businesses are
OL,7,Fbeing undercut by those not paying
OL,8,Ftheir fair share, while fraudsters and
OL,9,Fmoney launderers use and abuse the UK
OL,10,Fto aid and abet all manner of crimes.
OL,12,F"If we can deliver on this
OL,13,Frevolutionary manifesto, then we can
OL,14,Fonce again proudly say that Britain is
OL,15,F'open for business'."
